{"tid":124802,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"點解啲人可以咁on9？？？","createTime":"2017-02-18T02:32:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-18T11:01:58.000Z","uid":84072,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"80352667a8f6da1239f7fbd7d3b8e5f2a114d07f","tid":124802,"uid":84072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T02:32:23.000Z","msg":"話說我係O Camp同組識咗個女仔<span style=\"color: red;\">簡稱A</span>，之後都有保持聯絡同吹水。隨着相處時間多咗，咁熟絡嘅程度梗係多咗。跟住無啦啦我就發現左一樣野，就係有一個男仔成撚日我行過都望撚住我，初初我冇為意都係啲朋友同我講，我心諗可能佢哋睇錯。屌你老母，點撚知連續五六次都咁撚樣，有冇咁巧<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>交代下個男仔嘅背景資料：大概係O Camp唔同組，Disco night 個男仔搵左A去跳舞。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </strong><br />\n<br />\n之後俾我知道原來個男仔係成日搵A傾計，但係個A唔撚理佢，有陣時Hea鳩佢或者唔覆。所以我就諗屌你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你唔係咁on9 望撚住我係因為得不到的葡萄是酸的？有嘢就當面講啦男人老狗，望望望你碌柒？點解世界上可以有咁on9嘅人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最後我想講我都係冇理到佢，因為我覺得唔應該為咗一粒塵去花氣力，好似一隻牛唔會逐隻逐隻烏蠅殺死，因為隻牛知道係曬鳩氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<strong>真係好攞命</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d3115bda164fc7016cc3719c233ab0fc7a19900","tid":124802,"uid":71473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T02:33:24.000Z","msg":"你都好撚威wo！"},{"pid":"423a73402caa7121ce36122e8a0ea5fc7cd9ba38","tid":124802,"uid":84072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T02:36:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你都好撚威wo！</blockquote><br />\n真心覺得佢好撚煩<br />\n即係望我唔緊要（可能佢鍾意我？）<br />\n但係我唔喺度嗰陣時 佢都有望住我啲friend<br />\n心諗做乜鳩姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5436b32f07f7b59d781ddff93e1c583c55ea44f5","tid":124802,"uid":45772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T02:37:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4501ce68dbed280f7d18893ff2018d2a7dc79fec","tid":124802,"uid":71473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T02:37:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>你都好撚威wo！</blockquote><br />\n真心覺得佢好撚煩<br />\n即係望我唔緊要（可能佢鍾意我？）<br />\n但係我唔喺度嗰陣時 佢都有望住我啲friend<br />\n心諗做乜鳩姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n行過去問下佢點解成日望住你，佢就唔會望架啦"},{"pid":"8af2588207ae255155fc97a25b28804f76632571","tid":124802,"uid":21742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T02:40:24.000Z","msg":"所以話現今90後自我的膨脹唔係鳩吹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f948d06ab7649888047a103ab50a7f9dc39b51f","tid":124802,"uid":84072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T02:45:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>所以話現今90後自我的膨脹唔係鳩吹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好人好姐點會我每次行過都望住我？<br />\n仲要有次望足20秒<br />\n你鍾意話我喺度打飛機咪打飛機囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6bd5155da5b2398d7add4de1ee4bd2553c8fb86","tid":124802,"uid":6959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T03:06:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"37432d6cd965140c921a7913811cd68431eba8c6","tid":124802,"uid":76105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T11:01:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}